### Sūra CVIII.

### *Kau<u>th</u>ar*, or Abundance.

*In the name of God, Most Gracious,  
Most Merciful.*

1\. To thee have We  
Granted the Fount  
(of Abundance).

2\. Therefore to thy Lord  
Turn in Prayer  
And Sacrifice.

3\. For he who hateth thee,—  
*He* will be cut off  
(From Future Hope).

